
These are steps needed to make it work for windows authentication. Do this only in CRM development server. To complete development without deploying to CRM.

1) Enable cors on CRM server IIS.
  a) Add HTTP header
    Access-Control-Allow-Credentials   Value: true
    Access-Control-Allow-Origin Value: http://localhost:4200 (Default for angular- DON'T ADD this).
 2) Update this line in XrmService.
    let options = new RequestOptions({ headers: headers, withCredentials:true });


Run it: ng serve .it works
    
